## What happened

java.lang.NullPointerException encountered while launching the app in debug mode on the connected iOS device.

The error was in the Android Studio.

The app launched successfully though. 

## Version information

Tools • Dart 2.5.0

comment_data.body:
This issue was fixed in the latest release. Please update your plugin to the latest 40.2 
 Thanks.

title: java.lang.NullPointerException encountered while launching the app in debug mode on the connected  iOS device.
